div.p:
The next part will be the harder of the Two;
But yet in that we shall have Two chief points to
guid us.

First, False Rumours raised; Scandals divulged;
Jealousies fomented; Gods Anointed in his
Footsteps standered.

Then, Routs approved of; Arms taken up;
VVars levied; Gods VVord rejected; Gods
Sword resisted.
